<subSubSection id="B6DC9EABFFF1FFABFCB473EEDD4CF782" pageId="64" pageNumber="77" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="FE79CD20FFF1FFABFCB473EEDD4CF782" blockId="64.[831,1437,1737,2050]" pageId="64" pageNumber="77">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF1FFABFCB473EEDBD6F962" bold="true" box="[831,942,1737,1761]" pageId="64" pageNumber="77">Comment</emphasis>
: 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF1FFABFC3773EEDCFCF962" authorityName="DVORAK" authorityYear="1988" box="[956,1156,1737,1761]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Drusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="64" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zyrasoides">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF1FFABFC3773EEDCFCF962" box="[956,1156,1737,1761]" italics="true" pageId="64" pageNumber="77">Drusilla zyrasoides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described from 
<collectingCountry id="86D18DB0FFF1FFABFAEC73EEDB09F882" name="Vietnam" pageId="64" pageNumber="77">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
; the type material was studied and illustrated earlier (
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF1FFABFCC2722EDB9AF8A2" author="ASSING, V." box="[841,994,1801,1825]" pageId="64" pageNumber="77" pagination="1257 - 1282" refId="ref76789" refString="ASSING, V. 2015 d: On the Lomechusini fauna of Vietnam (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Aleocharinae). - Linzer Biologische Beitrage 47 (2): 1257 - 1282." type="journal article" year="2015">ASSING 2015d</bibRefCitation>
). The original description of 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF1FFABFA87722DDDE5F8A2" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2004" box="[1292,1437,1801,1825]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Drusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="64" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="truncatella">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF1FFABFA87722DDDE5F8A2" box="[1292,1437,1801,1825]" italics="true" pageId="64" pageNumber="77">D. truncatella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is based on a single female from “W 
<collectingCountry id="86D18DB0FFF1FFABFB51720EDD42F8C2" box="[1242,1338,1833,1857]" name="Malaysia" pageId="64" pageNumber="77">Malaysia</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingRegion id="3C0203C2FFF1FFABFACC720EDDE0F8C2" box="[1351,1432,1833,1857]" country="Malaysia" name="Pahang" pageId="64" pageNumber="77">Pahang</collectingRegion>
, Cameron Highlands, Tanah Rata” (
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF1FFABFB36726EDD4BF8E2" author="PACE, R." box="[1213,1331,1865,1889]" pageId="64" pageNumber="77" pagination="243 - 302" refId="ref77907" refString="PACE, R. 2004: Aleocharinae di Thailandia, Cambogia, Laos e Malaysia (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Belgian Journal of Entomology 6: 243 - 302." type="journal article" year="2004">PACE 2004</bibRefCitation>
). According to the drawings of the female primary and secondary sexual characters (
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF1FFABFB8872AEDC0DF822" author="PACE, R." box="[1027,1141,1929,1953]" pageId="64" pageNumber="77" pagination="243 - 302" refId="ref77907" refString="PACE, R. 2004: Aleocharinae di Thailandia, Cambogia, Laos e Malaysia (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Belgian Journal of Entomology 6: 243 - 302." type="journal article" year="2004">PACE 2004</bibRefCitation>
: figures 133–134), the 
<typeStatus id="217D7382FFF1FFABFAE872AEDB15F841" pageId="64" pageNumber="77">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF1FFABFC17728DDC53F842" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2004" box="[924,1067,1961,1985]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Drusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="64" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="truncatella">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF1FFABFC17728DDC53F842" box="[924,1067,1961,1985]" italics="true" pageId="64" pageNumber="77">D. truncatella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is undoubtedly conspecific with 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF1FFABFCB472EDDBB1F862" authorityName="DVORAK" authorityYear="1988" box="[831,969,1993,2017]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Drusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="64" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zyrasoides">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF1FFABFCB472EDDBB1F862" box="[831,969,1993,2017]" italics="true" pageId="64" pageNumber="77">D. zyrasoides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; for comparison see figures 43, 49 in 
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF1FFABFAC672EEDBEEF782" author="ASSING, V." pageId="64" pageNumber="77" pagination="1257 - 1282" refId="ref76789" refString="ASSING, V. 2015 d: On the Lomechusini fauna of Vietnam (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Aleocharinae). - Linzer Biologische Beitrage 47 (2): 1257 - 1282." type="journal article" year="2015">ASSING (2015d)</bibRefCitation>
. Hence the synonymy proposed above.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
